### Exercise 4


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
pop <- c(3, 5, 6, 6, 8, 11, 13, 15, 19, 20)
N <- 10^4
Xbar <- numeric(N)

for (i in 1:N)
{
 samp <- sample(pop, 4, replace = TRUE)
 Xbar[i] <- mean(samp)
}

ggplot() + geom_histogram(aes(Xbar), bins = 10)
```

